<div class="register container">
<div class="row">
  <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissable">
    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
    <span class="message"></span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="col-md-6"><h3>Sign Up For Free, It's Easy As Pie</h2>
<h5>Here's how you start - </h5>
<ol>
<li>Create a Hoopla.io user account here.</li>
<li>Log in and add your business profile.</li>
<li>Connect your social media networks if you'd like.</li>
<li>Create your events.</li>
<li>Generate a website widget for your website.</li>
